; Coverage test for op.cc O_QUERY (ternary) calc path (lines 374-381)
; Tests the ternary ? : operator in expressions.
; Exercises both the true and false paths of the ternary.

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Rent
    Expenses:Rent             $500.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --display 'amount > 0 ? 1 : 0'
24-Jan-01 Groceries             Expenses:Food                $50.00       $50.00
24-Jan-02 Rent                  Expenses:Rent               $500.00      $500.00
end test
